              or negative. Apart from 0, the values of the z-index can be:
              <br />
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <b>Auto: </b>The stack order will be set equal to the parent.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <b>Number: </b>The number can be positive or negative. It
                  defines the stack order.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <b>Initial: </b>The default value of 0 is set to the property.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <b>Inherit: </b>The properties are inherited from the parent.
                </li>
              </ul>
